title: The Mad Hatters #37 Sneak Preview: The Curious Mind of George Kimmel!
description: Thank you for tuning in for another fun sneak preview of the Secret Society of The Mad Hatters from the Tin Foil Hat Patreon Channel.  This episode we dive deep into the dangerous mind of Tiger Belly's and The Steebee Weebbe Show's,  George Kimmel! We find out what pushed George to the edge and compelled him to send Bobby Lee a pink dick dick pic. Fight fire with fire my friend.  All of this and more can be found on the Tin Foil Hat Secret Society of The Mad Hatters patreon.  We appreciate your support.
